<b>aka-chan dango wa itsumo shiawase no naka de</b>  

00:22:39.330 --> 00:22:47.800
<b>赤ちゃんだんごはいつも幸せの中で</b>  

00:22:39.330 --> 00:22:47.800
<b>Bebek dango her zaman mutluluk içinde.</b>  

